# Important Files

This file lists the important files for the MCP server project:

- `.cursor/rules/important-files.mdc`: This file, tracking important project files
- `package.json`: Project configuration and dependencies
- `tsconfig.json`: TypeScript configuration
- `src/main.ts`: Main entry point for the MCP server
- `src/github.ts`: GitHub API integration functions
- `.env`: Environment variables (not tracked in git)
- `.gitignore`: Git ignore rules

Note: If new important files are added to the project, they should be added to this list. 